<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>pawrequest</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
  
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        /* Apply Montserrat font to all elements */
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #343a40;
        }

        .jumbotron {
            background: url('background-image.jpg') center/cover;
            color: #000;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .features {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .feature-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
        }
        img {
            width:100%;
            height:600px;
            image-resolution:inherit;
            image-rendering: optimizeQuality; /* Modern browsers */
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; /* Old IE */
            object-fit:fill;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .accordion {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .accordion-item {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .accordion-header {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: left;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .accordion-content {
            padding: 10px;
            display: none;
            
        }
        .questions-container{
            display: flex;
            width: 50%;
            height: auto;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            margin:50px auto;
            max-height: 1000px;
            
        }
        #faq-header{
            display: block;
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    
<!-- Navbar -->
<%- include('header.ejs') %>
<!-- Jumbotron -->
<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" > 
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/mobile/000/046/895/huh_cat.jpg" alt="First slide">
        <span class="carousel-caption">Cats, masters of the art of relaxation, effortlessly transform any space into their personal sanctuary. With a soothing purr and velvety fur, these enigmatic creatures bring a sense of calm to their surroundings, offering moments of tranquility in a fast-paced world.</span>
    </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Orange_tabby_cat_sitting_on_fallen_leaves-Hisashi-01A.jpg/168px-Orange_tabby_cat_sitting_on_fallen_leaves-Hisashi-01A.jpg" alt="Second slide">
        <span class="carousel-caption">Agile hunters and gentle companions, cats navigate the delicate balance between independence and affection. From the mesmerizing flick of their tails to the gentle kneading of their paws, these mysterious beings communicate a language of their own, forming unique and cherished connections with those who are fortunate enough to share their lives.
        </span>
    </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/25/Siam_lilacpoint.jpg/221px-Siam_lilacpoint.jpg" alt="Third slide">
        <span class="carousel-caption">Cats, known for their enigmatic charm and independent spirit, have been cherished companions for centuries. With their graceful movements and captivating eyes, these feline friends effortlessly weave their way into the hearts of those fortunate enough to share their homes. Whether playfully chasing shadows or curling up in cozy nooks, cats embody a unique blend of elegance and playful curiosity that makes them beloved members of countless households worldwide.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
<!-- Features -->


<!-- Call to Action -->
<div class="cta">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Terms of Service</h2>
        <br>
        <a class="btn btn-light btn-lg" href="#contact" role="button">Download</a>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Contact -->

    <div class="questions-container">
        <span id="faq-header"><h2>FAQ</h2></span>
        <div class="accordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header" onclick="toggleAccordion('question1')">What is Paw Request Hub?</div>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="question1">Paw Request Hub is a trusted platform for pet adoption and rescue.</div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header" onclick="toggleAccordion('question2')">How can I adopt a pet?</div>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="question2">To adopt a pet, you can browse available pets on our platform and follow the adoption process outlined for each pet.</div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header" onclick="toggleAccordion('question3')">Can I donate to support your mission?</div>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="question3">Yes, your donations make a difference in the lives of animals in need. You can find more information on our donation page.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



<!-- Footer -->
<%- include('footer.ejs') %>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script>
    $('.carousel').carousel({
        interval: 10000
      })
      function toggleAccordion(questionId) {
        var content = document.getElementById(questionId);

        if (content.style.display === 'block') {
            content.style.display = 'none';
        } else {
            content.style.display = 'block';
        }
    }

</script>

</body>
</html>
